<h1> Select a Move to Add </h1>

<p class="well">
Every move available here is possible to combo into from the latest move. The
only consideration that is missing is a higher level game mechanic that numbers
are not publicly shared called hitstun deterioration that is added to prevent
infinite combos. With this in mind, be sure to make sure the combo works in the
actual game before creating it here.
</p>

<% unless @normals.empty? %>
  <h2> Normals </h2>
  <table class="table">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Move Name</th>
        <th>Start Up</th>
        <th>Hit</th>
        <th>Recovery</th>
        <th>Hit Adv.</th>
        <th>Special Cancelable</th>
        <th>Super Cancelable</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <%= render @normals	%>
    </tbody>
  </table>
<% end %>

